nodes.title: JDCN - Custom Nodes
widgets_values:
Seamless Node Used from here: 
Install from here: https://github.com/daxcay/ComfyUI-JDCN

These are new Custom nodes, made for the workflows made for patreon.

My Other Workflows and Documented Tutorial: 

https://www.patreon.com/jerrydavos


Node Workflow By 
davos.jerry+contactai@gmail.com 
Jerry Davos
This workflow takes an input image folder which has overlapping frames enabled. And will save them in a new folder inside the inputted folder location named "Output"

nodes.title: Seamless Settings
widgets_values:
BatchSize: Input the same batch range inputted in render workflow.

Overlap: Input the overlapping value inputted in render workflow.
